[14] A module ID of 778(0x30A) in 'wfHwEntry.wfHwModIdOpt' indicates the presence of a PCI PMC carrier card. The carrier card can have 2 PMC cards attached to it. For PMC card module IDs, refer to 'wfHwModuleEntry.wfHwModuleModIdOpt' for details.
